        public static Model build(Jobs jobs,
                          TypeModel typeModel,
                          TMax tMax,

        Build a Model with all option available except for the grid generation disabled by default. Encapsulate the resulting MIP, LP or CP model in a higher abstraction. in order to treat MIP, LP and CP model as undifferentiated model.

        public static Model build(Jobs jobs,

        typeModel - Type of the model to build.
        tMax - Tmax model.
